comments.content: [King Cool LC](http://web.archive.org/web/20081009203242/http:/www.dafont.com/king-cool-kc.font?nb_ppp=50&af=on&text=COUNTRY+DEPARTED) by Kimberly Geswein. One of the more famous fonts from the free/shareware department.Looks nice in this sample.

Nice one, Renko!  
The other one could be [TheSans](http://web.archive.org/web/20081009203242/http:/www.fontshop.com/search/?q=thesans), but the sample is really too small to say for sure.

The Sans below is a little small but it looks like …well [The Sans](http://web.archive.org/web/20081009203242/http:/www.identifont.com/show?L6).

EDIT: Woopsie, late. Aaand …danke, Florian.
